{"tid":1369263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實無分化，九成人都講緊同一樣野。","createTime":"2019-07-26T16:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T15:03:22.000Z","uid":173814,"like":324,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"8980f45d0d396f2c5ebc8aaef2d029f5c5c7fce1","tid":1369263,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:05:20.000Z","msg":"九成勇武和理非都贊成不入村主動進攻，但有人襲擊必定全力還拖。<br />\n<br />\n只係有少部分勇武想燒村燒祠堂見黑社會就打，有少部分和理非接受被打不還拖。<br />\n<br />\n事實係，係十幾萬人既運動入面，本來就無可能人人一樣想法。聽日小規模衝突實有，大家記住心中把尺就夠。<br />\n<br />\n我地互相尊重互相信任，不互屌不捉鬼，聽日做你自己覺得對運動有利既事就得。<br />\n<br />\n祝大家武運亨通。"},{"pid":"5a379c172b561f3acad24a4d1268e36fedf2c31e","tid":1369263,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b4001c06a2134bc4be1fae782d5a247a7846c45","tid":1369263,"uid":279616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0a3b8955c6996596c4a9e7d3d4cf0c2d3e328b9","tid":1369263,"uid":173814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a379c172b561f3acad24a4d1268e36fedf2c31e","tid":1369263,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:06:00.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"我見好多人嘈緊一樣既野，感覺有d奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩邊講一樣既野架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69937d5111f1ff2bedf8b348d2e59025955363b2","tid":1369263,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"或加達<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或加達<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或加達<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或加達<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或加達<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或加達<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或加達<im